{"id": 1734, "genre": 1001, "title": "把线下店当试衣间的时候你都有啥尴尬时刻？", "description": "各种消费报告都说现如今人们已经习惯在线下店选购、线上下单的购物模式，但我操作的时候咋总感觉哪里不太对！（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 2033, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170608163920dncRmro6lFY40XjP.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-20T03:00:29Z", "options": [{"id": 214531, "content": "店员太热情，不买都觉得不好意思?", "image": null, "praise_count": 433, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919463}, {"id": 214534, "content": "优衣库", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970634}, {"id": 214538, "content": "还做过这件事", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121856}, {"id": 216330, "content": "试了觉得好看但是线上找不到…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056538}, {"id": 214539, "content": "拍的模糊的找不到，但是拍的清楚的更找不到。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195734}, {"id": 214544, "content": "总会找各种借口说我不买了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841628}, {"id": 214547, "content": "市场造就趋势：以后连锁加盟淘汰出市场，门店都是试衣间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017835}, {"id": 214548, "content": "在导购热情的服务下想出各种不买的理由", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659191}, {"id": 214550, "content": "诶这个问卷不是发过了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 214552, "content": "一直在试衣服，但是最后没买，超级不好意思，我感觉店员在心里已经把我乱枪打死了┐（─__─）┌", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057901}, {"id": 214553, "content": "傻傻地把前后穿反?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941992}, {"id": 214554, "content": "线上选款式，线下试码数", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699588}, {"id": 214555, "content": "一般试了，就得买", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211089}, {"id": 214556, "content": "该减肥了", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833468}, {"id": 214557, "content": "你们怎么都这么机智？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003934}, {"id": 214563, "content": "明明喜欢却得找理由应付导购", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475848}, {"id": 214565, "content": "强行挑毛病说服导购不买 然后转头马上搜马云宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815906}, {"id": 214570, "content": "挑的时候一副老娘买得起的样子，试完以各种借口跑掉，最后一般是找代购，因为专柜真的贵太多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059447}, {"id": 214572, "content": "太热情", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013934}, {"id": 214829, "content": "被白了一眼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914818}, {"id": 215853, "content": "试内衣的时候，店员一定要进来帮我穿！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062588}, {"id": 214574, "content": "别人换衣没锁门?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013301}, {"id": 215855, "content": "试的件数多，店员在背后说坏话:试这么多肯定买不了，光试不买，来过瘾的吧……拜托，就隔了一层布帘，我又不是聋子，下回议论声音请小点儿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997313}, {"id": 210992, "content": "试了半天，最后当着店员面在手机上下单，对方很无奈", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 214576, "content": "看好了一套衣服 试了一堆以后 买了店员推荐的一套", "image": "img/option/option/20170620143511hDfJPObNe4Tx26wQ.jpg", "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910557}, {"id": 215088, "content": "店员对你的态度吧，因人而异", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060896}, {"id": 210993, "content": "不好意思把型号记下来，回去凭记忆找搞不清到底试的是哪款", "image": null, "praise_count": 246, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 214577, "content": "生硬的找个借口说不买，什么尺码不对，不是想要的款式，最多的是说没有想要的色款……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117674}, {"id": 216369, "content": "不买有时老板还会生气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064636}, {"id": 214578, "content": "挺尴尬的，你去，只是为了看一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221934}, {"id": 220210, "content": "那些衣服什么人都试过…担心…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074717}, {"id": 210995, "content": "躲在试衣间搜海淘价，感觉偷偷摸摸的", "image": null, "praise_count": 187, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 214581, "content": "试到店员一直跟着直到离开", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222178}, {"id": 214583, "content": "拿了觉得自己能穿的号，结果还是穿不上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057553}, {"id": 214586, "content": "那如果把线下店纯粹是当成一个展示平台呢，主动提供商品二维码的线上购买链接，然后线上的盈利提成一部分给线下店？", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059516}, {"id": 214587, "content": "试完之后其实真的非常合适，怎么摆出一点的不适合的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451150}, {"id": 214588, "content": "目前只能在运动鞋和睡衣唯二两种品类上成功使用这种模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765001}, {"id": 222268, "content": "有时，明明对于服务员自身也是贵的，但是当顾客纠结于价钱高要不买时，服务员会有些不屑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279510}, {"id": 214589, "content": "应该尴尬吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057388}, {"id": 225853, "content": "是口红色号，然后柜台说，唉，xxx.你也不看这点，人家都要把你家店搬空了，其实我就是试了2个色", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024675}, {"id": 214591, "content": "有导购跟着的店不买不太好意思试衣服……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059546}, {"id": 214592, "content": "店员已经不带搭理你了\n  熟悉了你这张脸！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 214595, "content": "很满意一件衣服之后 偷偷拎出吊牌看尺寸", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015624}, {"id": 214596, "content": "店员辣么热情 只想在这试衣服的我不买很尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015624}, {"id": 214597, "content": "这位小姐，这条裙子你穿不了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048145}, {"id": 212294, "content": "一般试了，回去也不一定会买", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 382393}, {"id": 214598, "content": "拿了一件发现大小不合适，可是已经脱光了，还要叫人帮忙换号，自己就光着坐在试衣间里傻傻的等。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011002}, {"id": 212296, "content": "试了一大堆等着回去下单店员很鄙夷", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343138}, {"id": 214600, "content": "说真的，店员很热情帮我挑，还告诉我他们公司最近网络购物折扣很大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054488}, {"id": 212298, "content": "试了说不要了但是店员不停拿衣服过来，最后不得不找借口离开", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267334}]}